text: Obed Saúl Martínez Villarreal (born March 30, 1996 in Monterrey, Nuevo León) is a professional Mexican footballer who currently plays for Correcaminos UAT as a midfielder. He made his professional debut with FC Juárez during a Copa MX victory over Veracruz on 19 July 2016. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican footballers Category:Mexican expatriate footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:C.F.
